### Path Aliases & Imports

To maintain clean and consistent import paths, use the following TypeScript path aliases.

```typescript
@core/* // app/core/*
@shared/* // app/shared/*
@widget/* // app/widget/*
@domain/* // app/domain/*
@env/* // environments/*
```

### Import Examples
```typescript
// Core imports
import { AuthGuard } from '@core/guards/auth.guard';
import { AppLayout } from '@core/layout/app.layout';

// Shared imports
import { NotificationService } from '@shared/services/notification.service';
import { LoadingSpinner } from '@shared/components/loading-spinner.component';

// Widget imports
import { VButton } from '@widget/components/v-button.component';
import { VCard } from '@widget/components/v-card.component';

// Domain imports
import { EstablishmentService } from '@domain/establishment/establishment.service';
import { UserApi } from '@domain/user/user.api';
```